[Feature: Build the leave management module — Phase 1: Establish LeaveRequest model and repository]

Create approximately 4-5 files under src/modules/leave: src/modules/leave/leave.model.ts defining the canonical LeaveRequest entity and DTO/types used by persistence, src/modules/leave/leave.repository.ts defining the repository interface, and a PostgreSQL implementation file for LeaveRequest persistence. Include focused Vitest coverage for repository behavior. Keep this phase limited to persistence and type definitions; do not implement submission, approval, or rejection workflows.

Phase architecture notes:
Owns LeaveRequest persistence in the leave module. Domain model and repository are introduced together as required.

